Student Performance Predictor Project Report
Introduction
This project aims to predict student academic performance using machine learning techniques.
Objectives
To analyze factors affecting performance and build a predictive model.
Problem Statement
Identifying weak students early using data-driven methods.
Methodology
Data collection, preprocessing, model training, and evaluation.
Tools & Technologies
Python, Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn.
Implementation
Linear Regression model is used for prediction.
Results
Model predicts student performance with reasonable accuracy.
Conclusion
The system helps improve academic outcomes.
